TextEng: Stirge? You're one of the escaped criminals with a huge bounty on his head!
Text: 스터지? 네 머리에 엄청난 현상금이 걸린 탈주범 중 한 명이잖아!

TextEng: Stirge? You have huge bounty on head. Me want that money.
Text: 스터지? 너 머리에 엄청난 현상금. 나 그 돈 원해.

TextEng: A baby killer? In that case, I'll have to kill you.
Baby killer? Okay, me kill you den.
Text: 아기 살인자? 좋아. 나 너 죽인다.

TextEng: Do you say that to everyone?
Me wonders if you always say such stuff.
Text: 나 궁금해. 너 항상 그런 말 해?

TextEng: Wait. What were you even a prisoner for?
Text: 잠깐. 도대체 무슨 죄로 죄수였던 거야?

TextEng: Okay, how did you get out?
Me asks how you get out?
I'm done talking to a baby killer. Defend yourself!
Text: 아기 살인자와는 더 이상 얘기 안 해. 방어해!

TextEng: Me done yapping to baby killer! Die!
Text: 나 아기 살인자랑 더 안 얘기해! 죽어!

TextEng: So you went to the other inmates?
Your escape hasn't been a success yet.
Text: 네 탈출은 아직 성공한 게 아니야.

TextEng: Can you give me an example of how to play?
Text: 어떻게 하는 건지 예시를 줄 수 있어?

TextEng: Uh, me need example of how to play.
Text: 어... 나 어떻게 하는지 예시 필요해.

TextEng: Hurry up and give your ear gnome!
All right, how did you get out?
Me takes bait. How you get out?
Text: 나 미끼 문다. 너 어떻게 나왔어?

TextEng: You gets help from other inmates?
What kinds of talent they got?
You still trying to escape. No success yet?
Text: 너 아직 탈출하려는 중. 아직 성공 못 했어?

TextEng: Stirge? You're one of the escaped criminals with a huge bounty on his head!
Text: 스터지? 네 머리에 엄청난 현상금이 걸린 탈주범 중 한 명이잖아!

TextEng: Stirge? You have huge bounty on head. Me want that money.
Text: 스터지? 너 머리에 엄청난 현상금. 나 그 돈 원해.

TextEng: Why would you tell this to a stranger?
Text: 왜 낯선 사람에게 이런 걸 말하는 거야?

TextEng: Me wonders why you tell such stuff to stranger?
Text: 나 궁금해. 왜 너 낯선 사람한테 그런 말 해?
